    "### Distribution Comparison Interpretation\n",
    "\n",
    "The comparison between normal and faulty operation reveals important insights into how faults manifest in this chemical process system.\n",
    "\n",
    "#### 1. Faults Appear as Subtle Distribution Shifts\n",
    "Across most variables (temperature, pressure, conversion rate, vibration), the fault distributions largely overlap with normal operation. However, small but meaningful differences are observed in:\n",
